    "causal_summary": "Phase 003 of packet 035 (unified command-contract architecture). Design-first. The central restructure (plan-review GAP-58): every command emits ONE build-time self-contained typed contract the executor reads first — Gate-3 line, verbatim render block, output template, write boundary, receipts + progress contract refs, tool list, absorption-abort rule — with maintainers keeping layered sources behind a drift guard. Subsumes old render/agent-contracts/compiled/injection phases. Closes F-006/007/009/019/020/021/022/027/029/035/036/037/038/039/042. Absorbs GAP-02/09/10/42/43/46/52/53/55/56/57/58.",
